      "content": "but if they can make my blood thinner, then isn't that exactly what i want? if the warfarin is too much and making me bleed easy, wouldn't i just use the garlic and the smoothies to keep it at a good level naturally? just tell me how much i should be taking or eating to keep it steady so i can stop dealing with the pharmacy and the clinic every week.",
